IMPORTANT: This is an EXAMPLE license file
-----------------------------------------

To use NeuroInsight with FreeSurfer processing, you need a real license.

How to obtain a FreeSurfer license (free for research):

1. Visit: https://surfer.nmr.mgh.harvard.edu/registration.html
2. Complete the registration form
3. You'll receive your license via email
4. Copy the license content to replace this file
5. Rename to 'license.txt' (remove .example)
6. Restart NeuroInsight

License file format (5 lines):
- Line 1: Your email
- Line 2: Registration number
- Line 3-5: License keys

Once you have your real license, save it as 'license.txt' in this folder.
